OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening although chance of
OL,7,Fa little brightness in the far west.
OL,8,FThen mainly dry overnight with clear
OL,9,Fperiods in the west, a little drizzle
OL,10,Fpossible in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA largely cloudy start, but
OL,13,Fbright around the west coast and
OL,14,FWestern Isles. Brightening up through
OL,15,Fthe day with sunny intervals
OL,16,Fdeveloping for all. Warm, very warm in
OL,17,Fthe west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
