OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,6,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine
OL,7,Fat times, especially Monday. Very warm
OL,8,Fin the west with the best of the
OL,9,Fsunshine, cloudier at times in the
OL,10,Feast.
